  <fr:p>Let <fr:tex>u= { \mathopen {} \left ( \phi ,a \right ) \mathclose {}}</fr:tex> be an element of <fr:tex>\mathsf { L } {A}</fr:tex>. Note that <fr:tex>u</fr:tex> is equal to <fr:tex>\bigsqcup _{p: \phi }u</fr:tex>; as <fr:link
href="jms-001N.xml"
type="local"
addr="jms-001N">definedness coincides with positivity</fr:link> in lifted dcpos, we have <fr:tex>\phi  =  \mathsf { pos } \, u</fr:tex>, and so we are done.</fr:p>
